In order to show seamless EUCA<->AWS hybrid story I tried to create a very simple topology via visualops (https://ide.visualops.io)

After I created the topology visually, I exported it into cloudformation template which then after little modification (availability zone and AMI ID change) I tried to run on a 4.1.0 cloud with VPC.

